---
interface Props {
    user: {
        hasSignedUp: boolean;
        isAdmin: boolean;
        tasks: string[];
    }
}
---

Hello, ${user.firstName}. ${user.hasSignedUp ? "You have signed up for the event." : "You have not signed up for the event."}

${user.isAdmin ? `
You are an admin. You can do the following tasks:
${user.tasks.map(task => ` * ${task}`).join("\n")}
` : `
`}